"PlusOne" is a beautiful but also useful counter. You can create your own counting items with you favorite style, and track their changes persistently.

=== FEATURES ===

◆ Create counting items, with so many style combination;
◆ Review changes over time by line chart;
◆ Review and amend changes you make at some day in a calendar;
◆ Use Siri shortcut to update counting items;
◆ Use widget to update counting items;
◆ Share your achievement to friends with elegant image;

=== USAGE ===

◆ Habit formation;
◆ Daily punch;
◆ Event counting;

=== CONTACT ===

◆ E-mail: wen.pandara@gmail.com

Star Record is a recording APP with simple operation and various functions

【Recording export】
Support multiple ways to export recording files, complete recording of recording information, convenient and fast!

【Voice recording】
Exclusive sound quality processing, segmented recording, restore real sound quality!

【Audio Sharing】
Share audio through WeChat, QQ, Enterprise WeChat, DingTalk, Photo Album, Email, SMS, iTunes, NetEase Cloud Music, QQ Music, Weibo, etc.

【save locally】
Recordings can be uploaded to locally, etc.

【Multiple recording formats】
MP3, M4A, AAC, MP4, CAF, AIFC, AIFF, WAV

【Recording management】
Support deleting and modifying recordings!

